{"tid":981520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求幫手揾英文歌","createTime":"2019-01-14T11:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T16:39:51.000Z","uid":17502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"940d6231ac0060defd9a7d9a1a7e71c2fa9977d7","tid":981520,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"我只記得間奏嘅幾隻字同第一段嘅旋律，麻煩各位巴打幫幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我用la代替音，希望幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nla &mdash;&mdash; la la la &mdash; la la la &mdash;<br />\nla la la &mdash; la la la la<br />\nla la la &mdash; la la la la<br />\n開頭係上面呢段係重複兩次，之後我就唔記得啦<br />\n<br />\n間奏淨係記得<br />\nmy heart.... my soul.... la la &mdash; la la la la la <br />\nmy love... la la .....  跟住唔記得啦<br />\n<br />\n求下大家幫幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723b3fccae20224350456e8795dd0239b83a5fde","tid":981520,"uid":194671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"You&rsquo;re my heart, you&rsquo;re my soul"},{"pid":"6322556fca98a59e0a6f44ab0aee6cbf56fdea5d","tid":981520,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左膠畀唔到反應你"},{"pid":"7498320cebafd8eafdd46ad624a8bc78339a5749","tid":981520,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:17:03.000Z","msg":"1.歌手可能為哪一種?<br />\n  [男個人歌手/女個人歌手/男子團體/女子團體/男主唱樂團/女主唱樂團]<br />\n<br />\n2.歌曲大概偏向哪一種類型?<br />\n  [活潑/抒情/悲傷/搖滾/復古/演歌]<br />\n<br />\n3.歌手聲音或唱腔有什麼特色嗎? 還是聽起來特別像哪個你所知道的歌手呢?<br />\n<br />\n4.有沒有印象有唱到哪些歌詞呢? <br />\n<br />\n5.可否用你所知道的方式(例如簡譜)表達旋律呢?<br />\n<br />\n6.請問你是透過什麼管道聽到這首歌的呢?<br />\n<br />\n7.如果是看到MV得知這首歌 那可以描述一下該MV的內容嗎?"},{"pid":"e0a83da5adffd7f7c